snippet.title: BEHEMOTH 🥚 Announcement & Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing BEHEMOTH, our brand-new, “dodge n’ flap” arcade extravaganza, releasing Thursday, October 31 on Steam!

Become the BEHEMOTH as you fly your flock of baby chicks to safety while dodging deadly fruits and peck-uliar obstacles soaring through the sky! Collect candy corn to unlock tons of new cosmetics, utilize Very Powerful Power-ups™, and compete in daily leaderboards for highest score and most checkpoints secured!

Price: $3.99 (with a 10% launch discount!!)
Single-player

Wishlist on Steam now to be notified when your flock is ready to be saved:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3027260/BEHEMOTH/

https://behemoth.thebehemoth.com | https://www.thebehemoth.com
Follow us on socials! https://links.thebehemoth.com/

Music by Ian & Lee
